{"type": "article", "id": 26698, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2016-05-12T06:39:36Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 27493, "name": "Harvest Vases"}, {"id": 27494, "name": "IO"}, {"id": 27495, "name": "Moai"}, {"id": 27496, "name": "Jean Hanger"}, {"id": 27498, "name": "Studio & Friends"}, {"id": 27499, "name": "Claesson Koivisto Rune Architects"}, {"id": 27500, "name": "wisdom"}, {"id": 27501, "name": "STEELE"}, {"id": 27502, "name": "Tengdimai"}, {"id": 27520, "name": "Gordost"}, {"id": 27521, "name": "Fratelli Spirini"}, {"id": 27503, "name": "Steven Sal Debus"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 19, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702105755Z1lnUCkwzKqmugOa.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p>\n<h2>Harvest Vases by Studio &amp; Friends</h2>\n<p class=\"\">用蔬果种植花草会是什么样？<a href=\"http://www.studioandfriends.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Studio &amp; Friends</a> 的 <a href=\"http://www.studioandfriends.com/#/harvest-vases/\" target=\"_blank\">Harvest Vases</a> 给出了一个新颖的答案。这是一组兼具了实用性和颜值的花器，外形很像表皮被剥开的蔬果，花花草草从开口处探出头来的样子看上去特别可爱。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607180829ET2XlrYvPJMfsue4.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607180829b7GB1ztSoVeUQZya.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.72166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607180830vRC6ATXpodKU8jqD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071808302EowHsIeGSFL8vWm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.725\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607180831rR6ABKmtCSX8D73u.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607180831SEVvxDjrpu19itbY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.815\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h1>IO by Claesson Koivisto Rune Architects</h1>\n<p class=\"\">宇宙中的各类天体一直以来都是设计师们的灵感来源，<a href=\"http://www.claessonkoivistorune.se/\" target=\"_blank\">Claesson Koivisto Rune Architects</a> 设计的这款壁灯就参考了 1610 年伽利略发现的木星卫星 IO。它的外壳是一块弯折处理过的压铸铝板，从侧面看好像微微悬浮于墙面上，LED 光源带来的柔和光线则从两端和缝隙中倾泻而出。这个造型独特的灯具还可以通过内置的双重轴线旋转系统沿纵、横轴线同时旋转，自由调节光线的方向。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607180831Bqi5Qa8Sc0NKGdTZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607180832ckL69YeKpj2ZgSFX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71612903\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607180832PriLFOXJ1qb2xm5G.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75076923\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607180833CFlEfcOGVK2hQbYu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71770833\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607180833IvbdUJiPVzeqTNau.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.33333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607180834GpbQuLr1BHVolqR0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.33333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h1>Tote Bag by <span style=\"background-color: transparent;\">wisdom x STEELE</span>\n</h1>\n<p class=\"\">这个帆布托特包是台湾男装设计品牌 <a href=\"http://www.everydayobject.us/?s=wisdom\">wisdom</a> 与美国帆布品牌 <a href=\"http://www.steelecanvas.com/\">STEELE</a> 的联名作。箱型折边、底部双缝线以及侧边三角缝线补强的配置，保证了它的坚固与耐用性。无分割的大容量内层，可以自由收纳各类物件，底部还特意采用了明黄色防水面料。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<span style=\"background-color: transparent;\"></span><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607180834aN1YlDdjiUIZVW0M.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071808356scKLAYPMSzHWk1V.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607180835KGeoJUzcNRSgrmpj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607180836QcDTSwUGZiO1tegn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607180837JSkZ2eEzRcqMT3W6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607180837rDoU0elzmHyPgnY8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Moai by Tengdimai</h2>\n<p class=\"\">来自台湾的设计团队 Tengdimai 从复活节岛上的摩艾石像获得灵感，打造出了一款颇为“石尚”的喇叭。每件的外观均采用手工喷制，在原料中加入了细砂成分以呈现出旧水泥和石头的效果。底座部分则采用了磁铁附着的设计，可以轻松地收纳过长的电线，作为纯摆设时完全看不到外露的线材。石像的嘴巴被设计为耳机的插座，增添了一份喜感。这个喇叭目前处于<a href=\"https://www.zeczec.com/projects/tdm-moai\">众筹</a>阶段，售价为 1450 新台币。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607180838Uwd0LPJgZSubhs8T.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071808380Mp872xTdeNvHlOL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6675\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607180839zWRelNvGSU79B8os.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6675\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071808392XhLCxs7pIjtPuOe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6675\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607180840O8LmnFpXJ16vdqkS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6675\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607180840mRilMP79F2V1G0Z4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6675\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Jean Hanger by Steven Sal Debus</h2>\n<p class=\"\">丹宁爱好者们，如果你为如何正确收藏和保养牛仔裤犯愁，不妨试试加拿大产品设计师 Steven Sal Debus 设计的 Jean Hanger。这个牛仔裤专用衣架由坚固细木制成，不同于普通衣架的长度（19 英寸，约合 48 厘米）能够撑起大部分尺寸的牛仔裤，而且中间的钩形部分能够彻底将裤子展平，杜绝了出现褶皱的可能。目前这款衣架在 <a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/saldebus/the-jean-hanger-the-new-way-to-care-for-your-jeans\">Kickstarter</a> 上的众筹还在继续，唯一可惜的是不能寄往中国。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607180841fC4nERLtxopcSzy7.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.8\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607180841oay4fz39juL6KPGQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66627635\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607180842PAUynTezR5clkKwO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66597938\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071808424qI5ONmcos8Rjzu0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.41764706\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607180843gsp0iTrlad8CcwWP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.41764706\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607180843qALHusO8UCPZtaMJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.41764706\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h1>Fratelli Spirini Soft Cheese by Gordost</h1>\n<p class=\"\">还有什么比用牛来做奶制品的看板更合适呢？俄罗斯品牌 Fratelli Spirini 委托 Gordost 设计的软奶酪包装就是这么一个让人过目难忘的创意：除了将睁着水汪汪大眼睛的牛直接印上包装，还讨巧地设计了有着立体牛耳和牛角的外包装纸盒。如果你路过货架时一不小心和牛牛对上了视线，很有可能就忍不住把它带回了家。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607180843QPhfMoaKEJ94kOsz.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.707\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607180844DegSWs5pjUTCKmV7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.707\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607180844Gkzgj95QyvJi4tHs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607180845Kw5EkI4x0mLrFUaO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.707\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607180846SziYeaQr9FUubq5j.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.707\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}